{
  "stem": "25348.2",
  "chunk_idx": 10,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 9.5,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "It wasn't a huge hospital.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And I knew they were after someone more important than I.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] So I waited till it became more serene, and then I went out.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "I thought I wanted to avoid the main road.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And as I came out, [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] I was suddenly flattened to the ground by a huge Alsatian.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "It sounds like a story from the, from a fairy tale.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And when I looked up, I couldn't believe it.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "There was a uniformed German policeman standing over me and grinning.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "It was a roundup of Polish girls, recruited for work to Germany.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 4 SECONDS] He called the dog Rolf, and at that moment, I wasn't sure whether I was more afraid of the beast or the man.",
      "word_count": 27
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "Anyhow, I looked around, and there was a group of Polish girls, a couple younger than myself.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "The others were 15, 16, 17.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] And [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] they were on the lookout for the next victim.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "And I joined the girls.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "The scenery's changed, and your performance, your acting performance, had to change.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "You were an actress.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] So the girls cried because they had to leave their families.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "So I cried because not to invite suspicion.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 4 SECONDS] They brought us to a very crowded railway, Luck railway station.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 20,
      "text": "As we walked through the streets, all the Gentiles that saw us kept sort of crossing themselves.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 21,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] They saw young girls, you know, even though Polish girls.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 22,
      "text": "But I thought I'd defend my position because I thought that prospective Polish Christian workers were more worth to, to the Nazis alive than dead.",
      "word_count": 25
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 23,
      "text": "So I did as they did.",
      "word_count": 6
    }
  ],
